CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 13, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "Model Builders - Aircraft is fascinating for these boys, who usually make their interest positive by building model planes. Vincent Davis, Robert Tillery and Charles Martin of the Kay Boys Club are inspecting their handiwork. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Vincent Davis, Robert Tillery, and Charles Martin holding model airplanes in Kay Boys Club workshop
